we%20don%E2%80%99t%20write%20about%20what%20you%20can%20eat%20or%20where%20you%20can%20stay.%20We%20focus%20on%20the%20natural%20aspects%2C%20different%20species%20and%20the%20ecology%20of%20the%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mathi%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20understand%20that%20%E2%80%98travel%20is%20a%20calling%2C%E2%80%99%20not%20a%20mere%20trend.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20trying%20to%20replicate%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20and%20they%20think%20that%20is%20travelling.%20And%20for%20some%2C%20it%20has%20become%20more%20for%20pictures%20and%20social%20media%20rather%20than%20taking%20the%20experience%20of%20being%20in%20that%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinod%20observes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAdobe-Express-file-2025-03-03T161727.001_11zon-1741002075-500x666.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22wild%20orchid%20roaming%20owls%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAdobe-Express-file-2025-03-03T161727.001_11zon-1741002075-500x666.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAdobe-Express-file-2025-03-03T161727.001_11zon-1741002075-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAdobe-Express-file-2025-03-03T161727.001_11zon-1741002075-600x800.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAdobe-Express-file-2025-03-03T161727.001_11zon-1741002075-450x600.jpg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAdobe-Express-file-2025-03-03T161727.001_11zon-1741002075-300x400.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAdobe-Express-file-2025-03-03T161727.001_11zon-1741002075-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m