20on%20the%20internet%2C%20but%20I%20found%20just%20two%20images.%20Searching%20to%20find%20more%20information%20about%20Yazh%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20ancient%20Tamil%20writing%20through%20a%20few%20friends%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20from%20metaphors%20and%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharun%E2%80%99s%20breakthrough%20came%20when%20a%20friend%2C%20PG%20Saravanan%2C%20introduced%20him%20to%20classical%20Tamil%20works%20of%20literature%20where%20the%20Yazh%20was%20mentioned.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20to%20read%20works%20of%20literature%20like%20%3Cem%3ESilapathikaram%2C%20Seevagasindhamani%2C%20Tholkappiyam%2C%20Kurunthogai%2C%20Thirukkural%2C%20Natrinai%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20many%20more%20where%20there%20was%20a%20mention%20about%20Yazh%2C%20and%20I%20was%20completely%20hooked%20on%20the%20instrument%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20fascinating%20aspects%20of%20his%20research%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F253401%2Fkerala-peruvemba-mridangam-carnatic-music-instrument-kasumani-indian-musicians-family-legacy-history-tradition-culture-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeciphering%20the%20instrument%E2%80%99s%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20poetic%20metaphors.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20direct%20information%20about%20the%20instrument%20but%20rather%20it%20would%20be%20hidden%20behind%20%3Cem%3Euvamai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(metaphors%20in%20Tamil)%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tharun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhrases%20like%20%E2%80%98The%20sound%20of%20Yazh%20was%20like%20honey%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2